<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>:) اليَدَهُ: الطّاعَةُ والانْقِيادُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">! واسْتَيْدَهَتِ الإبِلُ:</span> اجْتَمَعَتْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>